{"tid":952784,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實每6秒1蚊係一個咩概念","createTime":"2018-12-23T12:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T13:31:24.000Z","uid":9269,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d72add70ee792158f9676efc9030e74babb378","tid":952784,"uid":9269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:07:57.000Z","msg":"我咁計<br />\n香港正常文職(唔計OT)<br />\n每日朝9晚6，8粒鐘<br />\n一個月返20日<br />\n如果用每6秒1蚊去計<br />\n10x60x8x20=96000<br />\n再簡單咁講，當你9粒鍾每日得3粒鍾有咸濕佬打黎<br />\n即係你飽讀詩書再出黎累積3年工作經驗<br />\n都可能唔夠隔住部電話呻吟叫春咁好搵<br />\n所以香港值得擁有幣少<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2dc3599764da6369920ad138908e525331e8c11","tid":952784,"uid":10277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:11:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6de822e1938f8056827028f89c90bd28c38a7d9","tid":952784,"uid":190066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:12:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28626df4626cd7b7e8f7459973ccc136e5abd4c9","tid":952784,"uid":23829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226e0a32c4398d85c11c35f2282682c4eb76e06d","tid":952784,"uid":125776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89aceb81af4b6ec61dc2263c4c23cb7c415bcfa4","tid":952784,"uid":172571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:16:25.000Z","msg":"樓豬 冇聽過以前啲咸濕